                <head>295. Minutes of a Senior Interdepartmental Group–International Economic Policy
                        Meeting<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d295fn1">Source: Reagan Library,
                            <persName corresp="#p_RRW_2">Roger Robinson</persName> Files, Subject
                        File, <gloss target="#t_SIGIEP_1">SIG–IEP</gloss> Meetings
                        04/28/1983–05/12/1983; NLR–487–6–44–15–1. Confidential. The meeting took
                        place in the Indian Treaty Room at the White House. No drafting information
                        appears on the minutes. Another portion of the minutes is printed as <ref
